Package de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.bo

Interface Summary
IBOOrder The interface IBOOrder represents the common attributes of the order purchase and customer.
IBOOrderItem The interface IBOOrderItem represents the common attributes of the order items purchase and customer.
IBOOrganization The interface IBOOrganization represents the common attributes of an organization entity.
IBOPrice The interface IBOPrice represents the common attributes for all price entities.
IBOUser The interface IBOUser represents the common attributes for all user entities.
 

Class Summary
BOAddress The business object BOAddress represents a address entity with it's common attributes like street, zipcode, city or country.
BOBaseUser The business object BOBaseUser represents the base class for all user objects.
BOCategory The business object BOCategory represents a category entity with it's common attributes like shortDescription, longDescription or parentCategory.
BOCountry The business object BOCountry represents a country entity with it's common attributes like name, isoCode or currency.
BOCurrency The business object BOCurrency represents a currency entity with it's common attributes like code and description.
BOCustomer The business object BOCustomer represents a customer entity with it's common attributes like customerId, name, address or companyName.
BODocument The business object BODocument represents a document entity with it's common attributes.
BOInventory The business object BOInventory represents an Inventory entity with it's common attributes like inventory, numberToReorder or thresholdReorder.
BOOrderCustomer The business object BOOrderCustomer represents an order entity of a customer with it's common attributes like orderNumber, orderDate, invoiceAddress or price.
BOOrderItemCustomer The business object BOOrderItemCustomer represents an order item entity with it's common attributes like orderNumber, amount, orderUnit or price.
BOOrderItemPurchase The business object BOOrderItemPurchase represents a order item entity with it's common attributes like orderNumber, amount, orderUnit or price.
BOOrderPurchase The business object BOOrderPurchase represents a order purchase entity with it's common attributes like orderNumber, orderDate, invoiceAddress or price.
BOProduct The business object BOProduct represents a product entity with it's common attributes like materialNumber, description, price, type or category.
BOPurchasePrice The business object BOPurchasePrice represents a purchase price entity with it's common attributes like amount, priceType, taxRate or country.
BOSalesPrice The business object BOSalesPrice represents a sales price entity with it's common attributes like amount, priceType, taxRate or country.
BOSupplier The business object BOSupplier represents a supplier entity with it's common attributes like supplierNumber, name, address or company.
BOUserCustomer The business object BOUserCustomer represents a user customer entity with it's common attributes like name, login, address or email.
BOUserInternal The business object BOUserInternal represents a user internal entity with it's common attributes like name, login, address or email.
BOUserSupplier The business object BOUserSupplier represents a user supplier entity with it's common attributes like name, login, address or email.
